{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857575020,"sessionID":"ses_286a49312ffemU3qSvKZfL7QjS","part":{"id":"prt_d795bb9980014LG9E6XFTObitr","messageID":"msg_d795b78a5001kiHYs3lipFcsZZ","sessionID":"ses_286a49312ffemU3qSvKZfL7QjS","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_c4c0ece284f04cf5a53d75cc","state":{"status":"error","input":{"content":"# Proposal: AR-024 — DockerService 封装\n\n## Summary\n\n封装 Docker SDK 交互层，提供镜像构建、推送、查询、删除等核心能力的统一服务接口，供 BuildRuntime 和 PublishRuntime 调用。\n\n## Problem Statement\n\n当前 CLI 工具需要与 Docker 引擎交互完成镜像生命周期管理（构建、打标、推送、删除），但缺乏统一的服务层封装。需要在 `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` 中实现 `DockerService` 类，将 Docker SDK 调用抽象为可测试、可复用的服务方法。\n\n## Design\n\n### 类结构\n\n```python\nclass DockerService:\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None\n    def check_docker_available(self) -> bool\n    def build_image(\n        self,\n        dockerfile_path: Path,\n        context_path: Path,\n        image_name: str,\n        tag: str = \"latest\",\n        build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n    ) -> Dict[str, str]\n    def get_image_info(self, image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]\n    def _get_image_info(self, image_name: str) -> Dict[str, str]\n    def _format_size(self, size_bytes: int) -> str\n    def push_image(\n        self,\n        image_name: str,\n        registry_url: Optional[str] = None,\n        username: Optional[str] = None,\n        password: Optional[str] = None,\n    ) -> Dict[str, str]\n    def _docker_login_sdk(self, registry: Optional[str], username: str, password: str) -> None\n    def _tag_image_sdk(self, source_image: str, target_image: str) -> None\n    def remove_image(self, image_name: str) -> bool\n```\n\n### 核心方法设计\n\n#### `check_docker_available()`\n- 调用 `docker.from_env()` 初始化客户端\n- 通过 `client.ping()` 验证 Docker 守护进程可用\n- 返回 `bool`，失败时记录日志并返回 `False`\n\n#### `build_image()`\n- 参数：Dockerfile 路径、构建上下文路径、镜像名、标签、可选构建参数\n- 调用 `client.images.build()` 执行构建\n- 支持 `buildargs` 传入代理等配置\n- 返回字典：`{image_name, image_id, image_size, build_time}`\n- 构建完成后自动打标 `{image_name}:{tag}`\n\n#### `push_image()`\n- 可选 registry URL 和凭证\n- 若提供 username/password，先调用 `_docker_login_sdk()` 登录\n- 若指定 registry_url，调用 `_tag_image_sdk()` 重新打标\n- 流式读取推送日志，记录进度\n- 返回字典：`{pushed_image, push_time}`\n\n#### `get_image_info()` / `_get_image_info()`\n- 查询本地镜像元数据（ID、大小、创建时间等）\n- 公共方法可添加缓存或额外处理，私有方法直接调用 SDK\n\n#### `remove_image()`\n- 调用 `client.images.remove()` 删除指定镜像\n- 成功返回 `True`，失败记录警告并返回 `False`\n\n### 依赖\n\n- `docker>=6.0.0` (Docker SDK for Python)\n- `rich>=13.0.0` (可选，用于进度显示)\n\n### 调用方\n\n- `BuildRuntime._build_local()` — 调用 `build_image()` 构建本地镜像\n- `PublishRuntime._prepare_local_image()` — 调用 `push_image()` 推送镜像到 registry\n- `PublishRuntime._prepare_image_for_publishing()` — 调用 `get_image_info()` 验证镜像存在\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n1. **创建 `agentcube/services/docker_service.py`**\n   - 实现 `DockerService` 类及所有公开/私有方法\n   - 添加完整的类型注解和 docstring\n   - 处理 Docker SDK 异常（`docker.errors.DockerException`, `docker.errors.APIError`）\n\n2. **更新 `agentcube/services/__init__.py`**\n   - 导出 `DockerService`\n\n3. **集成到 BuildRuntime**\n   - 替换直接 Docker SDK 调用为 `DockerService` 方法\n   - 确保 `check_docker_available()` 在构建前调用\n\n4. **集成到 PublishRuntime**\n   - 使用 `DockerService.push_image()` 替代内联推送逻辑\n   - 统一凭证处理流程\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n- 单元测试：mock `docker.DockerClient` 验证各方法行为\n- 集成测试：在 Docker 可用环境下验证完整构建/推送流程\n- 异常测试：Docker 不可用、认证失败、镜像不存在等场景\n\n## Risks & Mitigations\n\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| Docker SDK 版本兼容性 | 锁定 `docker>=6.0.0`，测试覆盖最小版本 |\n| 凭证泄露 | 密码仅内存传递，不写入日志或文件 |\n| 构建超时 | 调用方可设置超时参数，DockerService 记录构建时间 |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md"},"error":"You must read file /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md before overwriting it. Use the Read tool first","time":{"start":1775857575014,"end":1775857575018}}}}
